item.title: Annoying Error(NEW ERROR)
item.dc:creator: @Tico135 Tico
item.description:
@Tico135 wrote:

Alright it’s bugging you about your CLASSPATH. So I suggest you switch the variables.
CLASSPATH: CLASSPATH=C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_01\bin;%CLASSPATH%;
PATH: C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_01\bin

Also, it doesn’t like your music player. You may want to delete everything in the music folder.
